Sears,s,Store,Information,API,gives,users,access,to,information,related,to,Sears,and,Kmart,stores,This,information,includes,store,locations,store,hours,services,offered,customer,service,and,pharmacy,numbers,and,distance,to,a,specified,store,This,RESTful,API,is,JSON,and,XML,formatted,and,also,accepts,geographical,coordinates,as,an,input